@startuml UC_25_Ban_Mute_User
title UC-25: Ban / Mute User

|User|
start
:(1) Open the restricted users panel;
:(2) Select Ban or Mute for a member;
:(3) Enter duration, reason, and note;
:(4) Submit the action;

|System|
:(5) Validate moderator permissions and target user;
if (Ban action?) then (Yes)
  :(6) Store the ban record;
else (No)
  :(7) Store the mute record;
endif
:(8) Return the updated restriction state;

stop
@enduml
